parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Ouch, not just my legs, my whole body hurts... I didn't
realize continuing to climax could put such a strain on me.)
\nc<Senpai>I hope you've learned your lesson from this ordeal.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>O-of course! \bustMsgExp[1, 2] But, are you sure it's okay
to just delete the comments?

\nc<Senpai>All you need to do is listen to what I say, right? Now, I'm
off to a meeting, so get back to work.
\nc<Saki>What happened with the job evaluation issue?

\nc<Senpai>Apparently, the executive who brought it up just forgot
about it, so everyone's acting like it never happened.

\nc<Senpai>A cat in the executive parking lot scratched an executive's
car, so job evaluations are the least of their worries right
now.
\nc<Senpai>We should be thankful to the cat, shouldn't we?

\nc<Saki>Really. Who would have thought a cat would solve our
problems...\bustMsgExp[1, 3] I've always been more of a dog
person, but from today on, I'm a cat person.

\bustMsgExp[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>Then get back to work quickly, okay? If you don't listen,
you'll start crying again...
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eek! Please don't say things like that! Ugh...

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(It's way past quitting time... but what can I do... sigh...
this is going to be traumatic...)
